{{main|Shinhwa}}
This is the discography of the [[Korea]]n [[boy band]] [[Shinhwa]]. The group has released nine [[Korean language|Korean]] studio albums, one Greatest hits album, four compilation albums, 1 studio [[Japanese language|Japanese]] album, 3 Korean singles, and 1 Japanese single. The discographies from 1998 to 2003 were released under [[SM Entertainment]], while from 2004 onwards is under [[Good Entertainment]].
